           if        w-cnt-acc-ric-sel    not  = spaces
                     go to acc-ric-sel-999.
           if        v-key                =    "UP  "
                     go to acc-ric-sel-300.
       acc-ric-sel-400.
      *                  *---------------------------------------------*
